<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Journeys' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- Journeys Hero -->
  <section class="experience-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The Journeys</h1>
      <div class="experience-intro">
        <p>Every journey is tailored. I design each experience around you — your pace, your interests, what you need. We begin with a conversation, and from there I shape something that fits.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Journey Cards -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-cards-full">
        <a href="/journeys/rio" class="journey-card-full">
          <div class="journey-card-full-content">
            <div class="journey-card-label">4 days</div>
            <h2>Rio: The Soft Landing</h2>
            <p class="journey-card-tagline">A grounded introduction to Brazil</p>
            <p>Rio is a city you feel before you understand. It draws you in, but it can also feel uncertain at first. This experience is designed to remove that tension.</p>
            <ul class="journey-card-highlights">
              <li>Airport arrival and orientation</li>
              <li>Safe, well-positioned accommodation</li>
              <li>Movement through the city with awareness and ease</li>
              <li>Access to places that feel real, not touristic</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="journey-card-link">Explore this journey &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/journeys/bahia" class="journey-card-full">
          <div class="journey-card-full-content">
            <div class="journey-card-label">5-7 days</div>
            <h2>Bahia: Culture & Depth</h2>
            <p class="journey-card-tagline">Salvador and beyond</p>
            <p>Bahia is not one place. It's a region with different rhythms, from the intensity of Salvador to quieter coastal towns where time slows down.</p>
            <ul class="journey-card-highlights">
              <li>Salvador for culture, history and energy</li>
              <li>Coastal areas for space, nature and slower pace</li>
              <li>Food rooted in Afro-Brazilian culture</li>
              <li>Music and rhythm as part of daily life</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="journey-card-link">Explore this journey &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/journeys/nature" class="journey-card-full">
          <div class="journey-card-full-content">
            <div class="journey-card-label">3-5 days</div>
            <h2>Nature Reset</h2>
            <p class="journey-card-tagline">Mountains and coast around Rio</p>
            <p>Nature in Brazil doesn't sit far away. Around Rio, it's close and varied, from mountains and waterfalls to coastline and islands.</p>
            <ul class="journey-card-highlights">
              <li>Mountains: Teresopolis, Petropolis</li>
              <li>Coast: Paraty, Ilha Grande</li>
              <li>Water, forest and open space</li>
              <li>A pace that allows you to reset</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="journey-card-link">Explore this journey &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Begin -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How We Begin</h2>
        <p>Every journey starts with a conversation. I listen to what you want, how you like to travel and what you're curious about. From there, I design something around you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
